    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Prehistoric Iron Age culture, partially identified by characteristic pottery found on the East African littoral from Kilwa,Tanzania to the river Tana in Kenya.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
